---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Portfolio";
---

<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img width="300" height="259" alt="TechGif" src="/techgif.webp"/>
    </div>

    <h1>Welcome</h1>
    <div class="role-badge">
        <small>Quinten Epting | Security Engineer & Developer</small>
    </div>

    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
        I’m Quinten Epting, a <strong>Security Engineer</strong> at Pellera Technologies. My path to tech wasn't linear. 
        Before I was writing code, I spent years in <strong>Law Enforcement</strong> and the <strong>Military</strong>. 
        That operational experience gave me a distinct perspective on security—I know how adversaries think 
        because I’ve tracked them in the real world.
    </p>
    <p>
        I bridge the gap between traditional security operations and modern software engineering. 
        I don't just manage vulnerabilities; I build <strong>automation tools</strong> using Python and Go 
        to eliminate manual grunt work. Whether it's orchestrating <strong>Tenable</strong> workflows or 
        developing custom OSINT applications, I focus on building security solutions that are fast, 
        efficient, and actually work for the people using them.
    </p>
    <p>
        I am currently focused on <strong>Vulnerability Management</strong> and <strong>Threat Intelligence</strong>, 
        combining my analytical background with full-stack development to anticipate tomorrow's threats.
    </p>

    <div class="button-wrapper">
        <a href="/projects/">
            <button>My Projects</button>
        </a>
    </div>

    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <div class="link-images">
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Python" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/python/python-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Streamlit" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/streamlit/streamlit-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="MongoDB" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/mongodb/mongodb-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="React" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/react/react-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Netlify" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/netlify/netlify-original.svg" />
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="CSS" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/css3/css3-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="HTML" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/html5/html5-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="JavaScript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/javascript/javascript-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Git" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/git/git-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Go" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/go/go-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Kubernetes" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/kubernetes/kubernetes-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Docker" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/docker/docker-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="AWS" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/amazonwebservices/amazonwebservices-plain-wordmark.svg"/>
    </div>

    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
        When I step away from the keyboard, I'm usually in "dad mode." You can find me coaching my son’s T-ball team 
        or hanging out with my family. I’m also a massive fan of <strong>Star Wars</strong> and <strong>Power Rangers</strong>—universes 
        that keep my imagination active. I believe you have to keep a sense of fun and curiosity, 
        whether you're analyzing a firewall log or debating the best Ranger generation.
    </p>
</Layout>

<style>
    /* --- Global Width Override (Matches Resume) --- */
    :global(body) {
        width: 80% !important;
        max-width: 1600px;
    }

    /* --- Typography Overrides (Matches Resume) --- */
    h1, h2 {
        font-family: "Georgia", serif !important; /* Overrides Pacifico */
    }

    p {
        font-family: "Calibri", "Helvetica", sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    /* --- Headings --- */
    h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: #fdebf3;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        text-decoration: none; /* Remove default underline */
        border-bottom: 2px solid #78c2ad;
        padding-bottom: 5px;
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #fdebf3;
    }

    /* --- Light Mode Headings --- */
    :global(.light) h1 {
        color: #1e1e2e;
    }

    :global(.light) h2 {
        color: #2a5078;
        border-bottom-color: #2a5078;
    }

    :global(.light) p {
        color: #1e1e2e;
    }

    /* --- Role Badge (Small) --- */
    .role-badge {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    small {
        background-color: #584966;
        color: #fdebf3;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1rem;
        padding: 0.4em 0.8em;
    }

    /* --- Button Styling --- */
    .button-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    button {
        background: transparent;
        border: 2px solid #78c2ad;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: #fdebf3;
        font-family: "Georgia", serif;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        padding: 10px 24px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    button:hover {
        background-color: #78c2ad;
        color: #1e1e2e;
    }

    /* Light Mode Button */
    :global(.light) button {
        border-color: #2a5078;
        color: #2a5078;
    }

    :global(.light) button:hover {
        background-color: #2a5078;
        color: #fff;
    }

    /* --- Skills Images --- */
    .link-images {
        display: flex; 
        flex-wrap: wrap; 
        justify-content: center; 
        align-items: center; 
        gap: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .link-images img {
        transition: transform 0.2s;
    }

    .link-images img:hover {
        transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    /* --- Mobile --- */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
        h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; }
        
        .link-images img {
            height: 35px;
            width: 35px;
        }
    }
</style>